                    <span>This book did a good job in expressing what is needed for a manager to be effective. However,  I would also recommend reviewing the book Telecommunications Management by Nolan Vincent Jones for even more information regarding effective strategies to beat the competition.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">P.J. has enlightened us again</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
